name: 2 in 1
description:
Double expo shot on film. Bergen - Reikiavik
Two goats at Fløyen mountain in Bergen | Sun setting behind Höfði house in Reikiavik.

Höfði house is an historical building and owes its fame to is the 1986 meeting of Mikhail Gorbatsjov and Ronald Reagan. This event, marked the end of the Cold War.
